  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18-60 years old

          -  BMI 20-35 kg/m2

          -  Willingness to partake in an exercise bout

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Contraindication to strenuous exercise

          -  Clinical signs of chronic pulmonary, renal, hepatic, hematological, intestinal, or
             cardiovascular disease

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Smoking

          -  Recent weight loss (&gt;2kg in 6 months)
      </textblock>
